**x_train** contains "train/X_train.txt"
**x_test** contains "test/X_test.txt"
**x_data** contains x_train & x_test data

**y_train** contains "train/y_train.txt"
**y_test** contains "test/y_test.txt"
**y_data** contains y_train & y_test data

**subject_train** contains "train/subject_train.txt" 
**subject_test** contains "test/subject_test.txt"
**subject_data**  contains subject_train & subject_test data

**features** contains "features.txt"

**mean_columns**, **std_columns** contain info about selecting columns: colnumber, colname, coltype (mean/std)

**columns** hold list of indexes and names of selected columns

**x_data_final**  contains "activity_labels.txt"

**y_data_final** lists activity names for each record of data set

**data_final** keeps tidy data

**avg_data** is output data set 
